title: Trends in the COVID-19 Pandemic in Italy during the Autumn-Winter of 2020 (before Mass Vaccination) Compared with the Autumn-Winter of 2021 (after Mass Vaccination), Integrated with a Retrospective Analysis of the Mortality Burden by Age Groups and Life Stages in the Years 2019 (pre-COVID-19), 2020 (before Mass Vaccination) and 2021 (after Mass Vaccination): A Real-World Nationwide Study Based on a Population of 58.85 Million People
